data.description: This charming and quaint cottage boasts an abundance of charm in a truly unbeatable location! An intuitive floor plan maximizes space to deliver a decidedly open and functional living area. Large picture windows at the front of the home create an inviting space, omitting plenty of natural light. The master bedroom offers considerable closet and storage space for a home of its size. Benefit from an easy to access basement for additional storage and location of utilities. Alley access in the rear offers added convenience and potential for further expansion of the dwelling. An unrivaled location, just mere moments from BSU campus and the multitude of conveniences that come with such easy access to Broadway Ave. Density/development potential for a value-add play.
